text: The Young Swingers is a 1963 American musical comedy movie directed by Maury Dexter and starring Rod Lauren, Molly Bee, Gene McDaniels, Jack Larson. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1963 comedy movies Category:1963 musical movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Maury Dexter
